Student Side:-

Main Activity

StudentOtp 

RestaurantPage (displaying restaurant names)
subpart:- RestaurantCustomView

ItemsList (displaying item names of particular restaurant)
subpart:- ItemsListCustomView

ShoppingCart:- (displaying items in the cart with the sub total)
subpart:- ShoppingCartCustomView

PayUMethod:- (for payment)

BillingPage:- (displaying final bill of the customer)
subpart:- BillingPageCustomView

TransactionHistory:- (displaying order history of student)
subpart:- TransactionCustomView

StudentAccount:- (displaying student home page)

TrackOrder:- (tracking current order status)

Restaurant Side:-

Main Activity

RestaurantOtp

NewOrderActivity (displaying new orders to restaurant)
subpart:- NewOrderCustomView

AcceptedOrder (displaying accepted orders to restaurant)
subpart:- AcceptedOrderCustomView

RestaurantBills (displaying order history to restaurant)
subpart:- RestaurantBillsCustomView

RestaurantAccounts (displaying order history to restaurant)
subpart:- RestaurantBillsCustomView